{
  "texts": [
    "EEG devices could be added to evaluate the neural response of PTSD and to detect emotions.",
    "Both Desktop 6DOF and Standalone HMDs are recommended.",
    "In contrast, applications focused on military training should be Explorative with interaction, so that free movement within the environment is possible.",
    "The data collected by the biosensors could be used to adapt the task difficulty in real-time.",
    "The advised ones are those related to physical arousal and anxiety: HR, EDA and respiration."
  ]
}